Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.72,0:22:46.68,ED_CH,,0,0,43,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}我卻無法停止  Like a 癮君子
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.68,0:22:49.98,ED_CH,,0,0,43,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}再來一次 來吧再來一次
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.98,0:22:54.90,ED_CH,,0,0,43,,{\an9\fscx90\fscy90\fad(240,240)\blur5}出發吧 直到世界盡頭yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.90,0:22:57.48,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}走吧 我想去尋找快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:22:59.69,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}把鑰匙丟在家裡也未嘗不可
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:03.20,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}能夠活著笑著就心滿意足了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:05.78,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}即便身處一片廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.78,0:23:07.83,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}我也並非一貧如洗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.83,0:23:09.95,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}怎麼樣？All right
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.95,0:23:11.58,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}就為今天而亢奮不已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.58,0:23:14.04,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}來吧 我想在這個人間地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.04,0:23:17.42,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}跟你一起開懷大笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.42,0:23:19.67,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}隨心所欲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.67,0:23:22.26,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}來吧 若是一切都不復存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.26,0:23:24.80,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}故事就從這裡重新展開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.68,0:23:28.18,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}All right！盡情享受今天的精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.47,0:23:30.60,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}我們可以繞繞遠路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:32.89,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}也可以放聲你唱我和
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.89,0:23:38.27,ED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}直到世界末日到來
